commit_message: fix return wrong value when update cache groups
pull_request_title: Update Topology Cache Group Servers table to use AG-Grid
pull_request_body:
Closes: #6501 

This updates the "Cache Groups" Traffic Portal page to use AG-Grid instead of JQuery datatables. 

<hr/>

## Which Traffic Control components are affected by this PR?
- Traffic Portal

## What is the best way to verify this PR?
Make sure all the TP tests pass, make sure the new table looks okay.
